2004-10-22  Christian Persch  <chpe@cvs.gnome.org>

	* lib/ephy-string.c: (ephy_string_double_underscores):
	* lib/ephy-string.h:
	* lib/widgets/ephy-node-view.c: (drag_data_received_cb):
	* src/bookmarks/ephy-bookmarks-editor.c: (node_dropped_cb):
